'''Sachra''' was one of the largest gunsmiths working in the city of [[Tof Soren]] on [[Ord Vaxal]]. Sachra primarily produced [[Slugthrower/Legends|slugthrowers]], due mostly to a scarcity of the materials that were essential in manufacturing [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] and other energy-based weapons.

